file.name: common.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.2"
info:
  version: 15.3.0
  title: "Common Data Types"
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    Breed:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        family:
          type: string
    Colouring:
      type: object
      properties:
        primary:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Colour'
        secondary:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Colour'
    Colour:
      type: string
      enum: ['black', 'white', 'tan', 'red', 'blue']
